00:33:18,941 --> 00:33:31,412
if we offset the budget by $500,000 next year, or this year, and say next year, the budget alone increases by, I'm gonna make this up for easy math, because I'm not feeling well, an additional $500,000.

580
00:33:31,472 --> 00:33:32,733
We're behind a million now, right?

581
00:33:33,273 --> 00:33:34,274
We're behind $1 million.

582
00:33:34,314 --> 00:33:35,135
That's right, that's right.

583
00:33:38,706 --> 00:33:39,886
This has been ongoing.

584
