608
00:35:14,551 --> 00:35:22,093
Because if we do that, regardless of the fact that you're hiring more people and they have pensions, it's still less for us to do it in-house.

609
00:35:22,573 --> 00:35:31,258
So we can reduce the impact and we can reduce the amount of money we need to ultimately get the city where it needs to be.

610
00:35:31,278 --> 00:35:33,119
You know what I mean?

611
00:35:33,379 --> 00:35:36,001
Yeah, so Dave, both Dave and Dan.

